| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2906 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6733b4a4-3663-5ee0-9094-93926869d636"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
